  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You employ defensive martial techniques in close quarters, moving inside an attacker's guard. While you are wearing armor, you gain a +1 bonus to AC. Additionally, when an enemy within 5ft of you is about to make a melee attack, you can use your reaction to impose disadvantage. If an enemy misses when you use this ability, you can attempt a grapple or shove as part of the same reaction.</p>"
